MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 492

AMENDING PROCLAMATION NO. 16, DATED APRIL 27, 1922 WHICH ESTABLISHED THE CAVE FOREST RESERVATION ON A PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN CRYSTAL CAVE, CITY OF BAGUIO, ISLAND OF LUZON, BY EXCLUDING A CERTAIN PORTION OF THE LAND EMBRACED THEREIN AND DECLARING THE SAME FOR EDUCATIONAL PURPOSES

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby amend Proclamation No. 16 dated April 27, 1922, which established the Cave Forest Reservation on a parcel of land located in Crystal Cave, City of Baguio, Island of Luzon by excluding a certain portion of the land embraced therein and declaring the same for educational use of the Bakakeng Central Barangay, which excluded parcel is more particularly described as follows:

SWO-CAR-000683 Bakakeng Central Barangay

A parcel of land (SWO-CAR-000683) situated at Rurban Code 131102, Res. Sec. “E”, City of Baguio, Island of Luzon.

Bounded on the NE., along line 1-2 by Lot 113; MN-81 (portion) the Cave Forest Reservation; on the SE., along line 2-3-4-5-6 and on the SW., along lines 6-7-8-9-10 and on the W., along line 10-11 by an existing road right-of-way (10.00 m. wide ); on the NW., along lines 11-12-13-1 by Lot No. 113, MN-81 (portion), the Cave Forest Reservation.

Beginning at a point marked “1” on a plan being S. 64 deg . 51 W., 1,513.84 meters from Triangulation Station, “WRIGHT” B.T.S., thence:

46.69 m. to point 2;

11.27 m. to point 3;

34.90 m. to point 4;

24.07 m. to point 5;

8.49 m. to point 6;

3.11 m. to point 7;

9.68 m. to point 8;

41.45 m. to point 9;

14.39 m. to point 10;

24.42 m. to point 11;

17.25 m. to point 12;

37.43 m. to point 13;

30.13 m. to point of

beginning , containing an area of SIX THOUSAND ONE HUNDRED NINE (6,109) square meters. All points referred to are indicated on the plan: Bearing true; date of survey: September 27, 1994; Executed by Engineer Nicomedes O. Mogamog and approved on June 24, 2002.

The tract of land herein reserved shall be non-alienable and shall not be subject to occupation, entry, sale, lease or other disposition until again declared alienable by proclamation of the President.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 27 th day of October, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Three.

( Sgd .) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: ( Sgd .) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

